"count": 3225157, "title": "serial and government publications division", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=partof:serial+and+government+publications+division&fo=json"}], "partof_collection": ["chronicling america"], "partof_division": ["serial and government publications division"], "partof_title": ["baptist courier (greenville, s.c.) 1877-2013"], "place_of_publication": "Greenville, S.C.", "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "raw_lccn": "sn 82004649 ", "reel_numbers": ["00517016299"], "resources": [{"files": 16, "image": "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:scu:batch_scu_icaco_ver02:data:sn82004649:00517016299:1908020601:0084/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn82004649/1908-02-06/ed-1/", "word_coordinates": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service"}], "rights": ["<p>The Library of Congress believes that the newspapers in Chronicling America are in the public domain or have no known copyright restrictions.  Newspapers published in the United States more than 95 years ago are in the public domain in their entirety. Any newspapers in Chronicling America that were published less than 95 years ago are also believed to be in the public domain, but may contain some copyrighted third party materials. Researchers using newspapers published less than 95 years ago should be alert for modern content (for example, registered and renewed for copyright and published with notice) that may be copyrighted.  Responsibility for making an independent legal assessment of an item and securing any necessary permissions ultimately rests with persons desiring to use the item.</p>\n<p>The NEH awardee responsible for producing each digital object is presented in the Chronicling America page display, below the page image  \u2013 e.g. Image produced by the Library of Congress. For more information on current NDNP awardees, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html\">https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html</a>.</p>\n<p>For more information on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 13.96732, "shard": "04", "shelf_id": "sn82004649, 1908-02-06, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/scu", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["greenville county (s.c.)", "greenville county", "south carolina", "baptists", "greenville", "columbia", "newspapers", "greenville (s.c.)", "richland", "columbia (s.c.)", "united states"], "subject_headings": ["Baptists--Newspapers", "Greenville (S.C.)--Newspapers", "Greenville County (S.C.)--Newspapers", "Columbia (S.C.)--Newspapers", "Baptists", "South Carolina--Greenville County", "South Carolina--Greenville", "United States--South Carolina--Greenville--Greenville", "United States--South Carolina--Richland--Columbia"], "subjects": [{"baptists": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:baptists&fo=json"}, {"columbia": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:columbia&fo=json"}, {"columbia (s.c.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:columbia+%28s.c.%29&fo=json"}, {"greenville": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:greenville&fo=json"}, {"greenville (s.c.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:greenville+%28s.c.%29&fo=json"}, {"greenville county": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:greenville+county&fo=json"}, {"greenville county (s.c.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:greenville+county+%28s.c.%29&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"richland": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:richland&fo=json"}, {"south carolina": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:south+carolina&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2024-10-27T02:59:34.987Z", "title": "Baptist courier (Greenville, S.C.), February 6, 1908", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn82004649/1908-02-06/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn82004649/"], "batch": ["scu_eggplant_ver02"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1877", "description": ["Weekly Began with Vol. 9, no. 37 (Sept. 20, 1877) = n.s., v. 1, no. 1 = whole no. 416; ceased with vol. 145, no. 10 (May 9, 2013). Published in Greenville, S.C., March 20, 1879-May 9, 2013. Publisher: James A. Hoyt, September 26, 1878-May 28, 1891. Vol. 32-33 never published; v. 37-38 repeated in numbering. Issue for Aug. 12, 1900 called v. 32, no. 43, but constitutes v. 31, no. 43. Also issued on microfilm by American Theological Library Association. Description based on: Vol. 9, no. 37 (Sept. 20, 1877) = n.s., v. 1, no. 1 = whole no. 416; title from masthead. Latest issue consulted: Vol. 145, no. 10 (May 9, 2013). Courier (OCoLC)852795710"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:13.325Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn82004649/", "image_url": [], "index": 5, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [34.009286, -81.037094], "location": ["greenville county", "south carolina", "greenville", "columbia", "richland", "united states"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-81.037094, 34.009286], "number": ["duke univ libr", "online resource", "1776382", "2025-04-13t02:56:16.926058", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn82004649/1877-09-20/ed-1/", "sn82004649", "0744-6985", "original", "sn97064666", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn82004649/1923-12-27/ed-1/", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "1", "2398"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "baptist courier (columbia, s.c.) 1877-2013", "serial and government publications division", "chronicling america"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 94.910934, "shelf_id": "BX6201", "site": ["chroniclingamerica", "usnd"], "subject": ["greenville county (s.c.)", "greenville county", "south carolina", "baptists", "greenville", "columbia", "newspapers", "greenville (s.c.)", "richland", "columbia (s.c.)", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-07-18T09:02:06.495Z", "title": "Baptist courier", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn82004649/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2016271104/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1870", "dates": ["[1870 TO 1873]"], "description": ["Weekly Began with volume XVI, no. 38 (February 9, 1870); ceased June 11, 1873. Available on microfilm from The University of South Carolina. Merged with: Mountaineer (Greenville, S.C. : 1866), to form: Enterprise & mountaineer. Description based on: Volume XVI, no. 38 (February 9, 1870); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed June 8, 2016). Latest issue consulted: Volume XIX, no. 34 (December 25, 1872) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed June 8, 2016). Mountaineer (Greenville, S.C. : 1866) Enterprise & mountaineer"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:35.704Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2016271104/", "image_url": [], "index": 6, "language": ["english"], "location": ["greenville county", "south carolina", "greenville", "united states"], "number": ["2016271104", "online resource", "951407536", "2472-8942", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Enterprise"], "partof": ["directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "the greenville enterprise (greenville, south carolina) 1870-1873 [online resource]", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 57.099342, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["greenville county (s.c.)", "greenville county", "south carolina", "greenville", "newspapers