iler so the tractor can move off to another trailer", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2017849417/"}], "resource": {"fulltext_file": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/scu/batch_scu_icaco_ver02/data/sn82004649/00517016299/1908020601/0088.xml&format=alto_xml&full_text=1", "image": "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:scu:batch_scu_icaco_ver02:data:sn82004649:00517016299:1908020601:0084/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg", "pdf": "https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/ndnp/scu/batch_scu_icaco_ver02/data/sn82004649/00517016299/1908020601/0088.pdf", "segment_count": 16, "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn82004649/1908-02-06/ed-1/", "word_coordinates": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service"}, "resources": [{"fulltext_file": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/scu/batch_scu_icaco_ver02/data/sn82004649/00517016299/1908020601/0088.xml&format=alto_xml&full_text=1", "image": "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:scu:batch_scu_icaco_ver02:data:sn82004649:00517016299:1908020601:0084/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg", "pdf": "https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/ndnp/scu/batch_scu_icaco_ver02/data/sn82004649/00517016299/1908020601/0088.pdf", "segment_count": 16, "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn82004649/1908-02-06/ed-1/", "word_coordinates": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service"}], "segment_id": "/service/ndnp/scu/batch_scu_icaco_ver02/data/sn82004649/00517016299/1908020601/0088.xml", "segments": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn82004649/1908-02-06/ed-1/?sp=5"], "batch": ["scu_icaco_ver02"], "campaigns": [], "composite_location": ["0/united states/", "1/united states/south carolina/", "2/united states/south carolina/greenville/", "3/united states/south carolina/greenville/greenville/", "2/united states/south carolina/richland/", "3/united states/south carolina/richland/columbia/"], "contributor": ["university of south carolina; columbia, sc"], "date": "1908-02-06", "dates": ["1908-02-06"], "description": ["this we cannot knowingly assert for our people there have a noble and an honorable history But surely all will agree and his people lovingly assert it that Bro Mitchell is a workman that needeth not to be ashamed and that in the few years he has been there has accomplished a won derful amount of good Bro Mitchell is a native of New York State He was engaged in a successful and lucrative business from which he turned aside for the ministry He entered the Rochester Theological Seminary from which institution he graduated He was pastor in Nebraska and at Niagara Falls and Rhinebeck N Y From Rhineheck he came to Camden He was not a stranger in South Carolina when he was called to Camden as he had supplied the Johnston church for awhile He has attended several of our State Conventions and general meetings and has greatly endeared himself to his brethren in South Carolina who will rejoice with him in his success Next week we hope to give a picture of the new church and of its beloved pastor We greatly enjoyed our visit to Camden and we re gret that the stay was too short"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2024-10-27T02:05:03.120Z", "group": ["ndnp/scu", "university-of-south-carolina-columbia-sc-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn82004649/1908-02-06/ed-1/?sp=5", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:scu:batch_scu_icaco_ver02:data:sn82004649:00517016299:1908020601:0088/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=268&w=199", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:scu:batch_scu_icaco_ver02:data:sn82004649:00517016299:1908020601:0088/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=536&w=399", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:scu:batch_scu_icaco_ver02:data:sn82004649:00517016299:1908020601:0088/full/pct:25/0/default.jpg#h=1073&w=798", "https://ti